name: LAURA TEE
description:
Our new blue black LAURA tees are the first to carry our brand new Planets design, so go on a journey to outer space and grab one of these limited edition tees before they run out. The tees featured in the image are Lucid, Planets and Dreamcatcher but you can add any design to our LAURA tees simply check the details below.

The tees all come in sizes S M L & XL and are a unisex fit, for more sizing information check our size guide. Remember to notify us on what size you would like via email!

Please note when ordering CUSTOM tees you will need to specify what the design you would like is via our email at thesummerfox@hotmail.com, all custom orders must be specified and confirmed within 7 days of response via email or orders will be put on hold.

Wash with similar colours on the first wash to avoid any colour running, we always wash the excess colour before sending them out but for your care please follow the guidelines.
